- list the major components of the C++ standard library

C++ standard library consist of several components, which are contained inside "sublibraries":
* language support library
* concepts library
* diagnostic library
* general utilities library
* strings library
* containers library
* iterators library
* ranges library
* algorithms library
* numeric library
* time library
* localization library
* input/output library
* regular expressions library
* atomic operations library
* thread support library
